com.clover.remote.client.transport.usb.pos

Class PosUsbRemoteProtocolService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • com.clover.remote.client.transport.usb.pos.PosRemoteProtocolService
        • com.clover.remote.client.transport.usb.pos.PosUsbRemoteProtocolService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    USBCloverTransportService

    public class PosUsbRemoteProtocolService
extends PosRemoteProtocolService
implements USBCloverTransportService
    This service runs on the Clover POS device and connects to a Clover Terminal via USB. It stays up and running as long as possible so that it can deliver terminal status changed events to bound clients.
